'''Rakhine United FC''' ({{lang-my|ရခိုင်ယူနိုက်တက် ဘောလုံးအသင်း<!---UNICODE ENCODING, DO NOT USE ZAWGYI--->}}) Football Club is a professional football club, based in [[Rakhine State]], that plays in the [[Myanmar National League]]. '''Rakhine United''' Football Club in 2009, the club changed its name to '''Rakhapura United''' in December,2010. Home Stadium to use Waytharli Yinpyin in [[Sittwe]] Township, Rakhine State. Now they use to play in [[Thuwanna YTC Stadium]] as home. Last season Rakhapura United FC stand 10th position. Rakhine United FC biggest won (7-2) in General Aung San Cup against Manaw Myay.

