{{use dmy dates|date=July 2017}} {{Infobox sportsperson | name = Cuthbert Jacobs | birth_name = | image = | caption = | nationality = Antigua and Barbuda | sport = Sprinting | event = 200 metres | club = | collegeteam = | birth_date = {{birth date and age|1952|1|5|df=yes}} | birth_place = | death_date = | death_place = | height = | weight = }}
'''Cuthbert Jacobs''' (born 5 January 1952) is an Antigua and Barbuda [[sprint (running)|sprinter]]. He competed in the [[Athletics at the 1976 Summer Olympics – Men's 200 metres|men's 200 metres]] at the [[1976 Summer Olympics]].<ref name="SportsRef">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ja/cuthbert-jacobs-1.html |title=Cuthbert Jacobs Olympic Results |accessdate=13 July 2017}}</ref>
